{"id": 2157, "genre": 1001, "title": "你爸妈对你的刻板印象，你都发现了哪些？", "description": "“嗬！原来你能把自己家搞这么干净啊！”（题图来自：giphy）", "record_count": 3194, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180131171530sgwYdlITnRHKCQ4x.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-01T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 262912, "content": "不能吃辣，因为四五岁的时候确实不能吃辣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817838}, {"id": 263680, "content": "在家有人管着还这么懒，在学校没人管怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254981}, {"id": 262913, "content": "不能有太多钱，容易买乱七八糟的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251401}, {"id": 262914, "content": "每回打电话必说不要经常在外面吃不干净的食物，不要吃烧烤和零食，对身体不好巴拉巴拉。在他们印象里零食都是小卖部里五毛一包的，像三只松鼠这种他们直接忽略不计?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118986}, {"id": 262915, "content": "我妈：\"竟然还知道叠被子\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723753}, {"id": 263427, "content": "书读的不好就是不行?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689450}, {"id": 264451, "content": "出门拿个钥匙，我妈说小心弄丢了。出门拿个业主卡，我妈说小心弄丢了。下楼扔个垃圾，我妈说别带手机小心弄丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258820}, {"id": 262916, "content": "哎呦 知道穿秋裤了哇", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747017}, {"id": 262917, "content": "我就是背锅侠啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251409}, {"id": 263685, "content": "吃了粉丝/红薯/土豆/年糕类的主食不想吃米饭的时候，怪不得老说头晕/怪不得容易感冒?，饭都不好好吃，那些东西能饱吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254981}, {"id": 264197, "content": "懒一次，就给你定性了“懒”，之前的勤劳就跟忘了一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257750}, {"id": 262918, "content": "离开了现在的单位，不可能找到更好的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251413}, {"id": 263686, "content": "每次我说下班累得动不了的时候，他们就说在办公室的工作，全是闲呆着，一天到晚不知道你们有什么累的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123098}, {"id": 263942, "content": "不要以为你现在想的就是对的，我们才是经历风雨的人，你按照我给你说的做，肯定不会错！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256614}, {"id": 262919, "content": "不懂人情世故，自视甚高。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906056}, {"id": 262920, "content": "读了评论，发现我爸可能连“对我的连刻板印象”都没有，而仅是来自于社会上已存在的“孩子”形象的简单反映。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105318}, {"id": 263688, "content": "你感冒啦？都是因为不睡觉玩手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234521}, {"id": 262921, "content": "说我唱歌不好听？？\n然鹅在哪里和朋友出去我都是麦霸？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247718}, {"id": 262922, "content": "不管晚上是不是工作，父母都会叫你早点睡。不管冷不冷，都叫你多穿点。不管科普如何，都叫你不要喝可乐，别吃方便面。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691469}, {"id": 262924, "content": "玩游戏永远都是错误的", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208838}, {"id": 262925, "content": "脾气暴躁，不讲道理，然而我最喜欢跟人讲道理了\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735630}, {"id": 262926, "content": "粗心大意没脑子", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251444}, {"id": 262927, "content": "总是觉得我不行，不过至今为止我还没让他们刮目相看过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144137}, {"id": 262928, "content": "自己在外面吃的东西永远都是垃圾食品，永远不知道吃点好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248825}, {"id": 262929, "content": "永远觉得你吃不饱吃不好，捏着我胖嘟嘟的大圆脸说，哎呀我闺女又瘦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251372}, {"id": 263442, "content": "肥 不会做事 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033958}, {"id": 262931, "content": "只要我在家，就一定觉得我每天都要睡到中午才起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251510}, {"id": 263187, "content": "永远都在玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252622}, {"id": 263443, "content": "动手能力不强", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253612}, {"id": 262932, "content": "天天就知道玩游戏……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430476}, {"id": 263956, "content": "有妈妈在耳边唠叨是一件多幸福的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822007}, {"id": 262933, "content": "好吃懒做", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251512}, {"id": 262934, "content": "从小到大，有空不见得你看书，练书法。不知道为什么我妈妈特别执念，即使我毕业后加入互联网行业4年，目前写过的字不超过1000呀", "image": "img/option/option/20180201155917cd6v87NRlr9E2xtg.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251512}, {"id": 262935, "content": "像个女孩一样文静", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 432682}, {"id": 262936, "content": "放假在家永远都是玩手机，每天晚上自学学西语时查单词也说我玩手机?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227112}, {"id": 283160, "content": "自理能力九级残废~~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351739}, {"id": 262937, "content": "同一个世界，同一个妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229321}, {"id": 262938, "content": "在家待着不做家务就是在玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190286}, {"id": 262939, "content": "和别人家孩子比差的远了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984990}, {"id": 263451, "content": "“妈，我嗓子疼”“成天玩电脑玩的”(｡ ˇ‸ˇ ｡)", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253639}, {"id": 262940, "content": "别以为你不说我就不知道你整天在干什么、放的什么屁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251547}, {"id": 262941, "content": "无论如何，打电话给”我“就是出事了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251573}, {"id": 262943, "content": "“竟然能拎得动一桶水!??”? 我都20岁的男人了，一桶水拎不动吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251165}, {"id": 265503, "content": "整个人除了懒就是懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262816}, {"id": 262944, "content": "总是觉得我对什么都很无所谓，总是觉得我什么都不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094668}, {"id": 262946, "content": "你怎么那么懒!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948020}, {"id": 262948, "content": "觉得我特别乖巧听话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249996}, {"id": 263723, "content": "下雨了记得收衣服......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183746}, {"id": 262956, "content": "你快上一边去，你做不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232675}, {"id": 263469, "content": "永远都是懒的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182566}]}